The paper deals with clustering algorithms, which are typically studied in the computer science subfield of data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG). The problem of fair clustering also involves optimization and decision-making, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
